      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2015-01-22</actionDate>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-02-02T19:07:49Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2015-01-22T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Prohibits any prevailing rate employee in a federal agency, between January 1 and September 30, 2015, from being paid an amount exceeding specified limits resulting from an applicable wage survey adjustment. Prohibits the percentage increase in wages paid to a prevailing wage employee in FY2015 from being less than the percentage increase in the basic pay of other federal employees in the same pay locality. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
